Simple solution, create adjacency list like course schedule, include the starting word. Then initialize a stack with the beginning word. Use BFS as any word that have been visited do not need to be
visited again (because part of the chain already, and since visited earlier, part of the better solution). Use counter to keep track of the length of the chain. Cheers!

